The second part of this module is
really exciting because we will combine

47
00:02:56.570 --> 00:03:00.230
what you learn in module two and
module three.

48
00:03:00.230 --> 00:03:04.990
Remember that in module two,
you learn about Monte Carlo simulation,

49
